keywords rmlist
---
Syntax: rmlist list
        rmlist <modifier name>

Displays information about racial modifiers -- permanent enhancements that
can be purchased for your race using reincarnation points (RP).

  rmlist list       -- Shows all available racial modifiers with their RP
                       costs and any prerequisite racial traits required
                       before purchase.
  rmlist <name>     -- Shows detailed information about a specific modifier:
                       name, RP cost, prerequisite, and the affect it grants.

Racial modifiers are permanent and persist through reincarnations. They
represent deep enhancements to your racial nature beyond what class training
provides.

Examples:
  rmlist list
  rmlist toughskin

See also: reincarnate rlist qpspend
